) [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n43: 0x10449356c node::LibuvStreamWrap::OnUvRead(long, uv_buf_t const*) [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n44: 0x104493cb4 node::LibuvStreamWrap::ReadStart()::$_1::__invoke(uv_stream_s*, long, uv_buf_t const*) [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n45: 0x104f8f6d8 uv__stream_io [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n46: 0x104f97920 uv__io_poll [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n47: 0x104f84674 uv_run [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n48: 0x104286508 node::SpinEventLoopInternal(node::Environment*) [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n49: 0x1043c4154 node::NodeMainInstance::Run() [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n50: 0x10433a364 node::Start(int, char**) [/Users/rajpootathar/.nvm/versions/node/v22.14.0/bin/node]\\\\n51: 0x19f47eb98 start [/usr/lib/dyld]\\\\nzsh: abort      claude`\\\\n\\\\n## Steps to Reproduce\\\\n1. it hppenned when i ran any subagent in a project having really long memory saved accross files  and CLAUDE.md references then using `@folder_yft2/file`\\\\n\\\\n\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"name\\\":\\\"bug\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Something isn't working\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYeNg\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"area:core\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYe8A\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"platform:macos\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYfIw\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"memory\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYgjA\\\"},{\\\"name\\\":\\\"perf:memory\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYgjg\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":1,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T00:23:22Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T00:23:23Z\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4807017195,\\\"number\\\":8,\\\"state\\\":\\\"OPEN\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Symlink Hook Execution Failure in Claude Code\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"**Bug Description**\\\\n⏺ Bug Report: Claude Code Hooks Fail to Execute Through Symlinks\\\\n\\\\n  Issue: Claude Code hooks silently fail or hang indefinitely when configured to execute through symlinked directories.\\\\n\\\\n  Reproduction Steps:\\\\n  1. Create hooks in a project directory (e.g., /Users/user/projects/my-hooks/)\\\\n  2. Create a symlink: ln -s /Users/user/projects/my-hooks ~/.claude/hooks\\\\n  3. Configure ~/.claude/settings.json with hook paths like ~/.claude/hooks/pre_tool_use.py\\\\n  4. Attempt to use Claude Code - hooks will hang or fail silently\\\\n\\\\n  Expected Behavior: Hooks should execute normally through symlinks, as symlinks work for other file operations (reading, listing).\\\\n\\\\n  Actual Behavior: Hook execution hangs indefinitely or fails silently. No error messages are provided.\\\\n\\\\n  Workaround: Use absolute paths directly to the hook files instead of symlink paths:\\\\n  - ❌ ~/.claude/hooks/pre_tool_use.py (through symlink)\\\\n  - ✅ /Users/user/projects/my-hooks/pre_tool_use.py (direct path)\\\\n\\\\n  Impact: This caused hours of unnecessary debugging, as the issue appeared to be with the hook code itself rather than the execution path. The symlink appears to work for file operations (ls, cat) but not for execution.\\\\n\\\\n  Environment: macOS, Claude Code with Python hooks\\\\n\\\\n**Environment Info**\\\\n- Platform: darwin\\\\n- Terminal: vscode\\\\n- Version: 1.0.72\\\\n- Feedback ID: f1710d3d-8c74-45aa-845e-9883b8bd00ba\\\\nNote: Not sure the errors below are relevant. And I think I understand the first one. While refactoring agents for me, claude put documenation files in the agents folder.  I'll go move those. \\\\n**Errors**\\\\n```json\\\\n[{\\\\\\\"error\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Error: Agent file /Users/bpruss/repos/cdc/cdc-devtools/.claude/agents/DEVOPS_CONSOLIDATION_POC.md is missing required 'name' in frontmatter\\\\\\\\n    at OY8 (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_3ejg/claude-code/cli.js:2213:1812)\\\\\\\\n    at file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_u0j2/claude-code/cli.js:2213:333\\\\\\\\n    at Array.map (\\\\u003canonymous\\\\u003e)\\\\\\\\n    at file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_ypgi/claude-code/cli.js:2213:269\\\\\\\\n    at async file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_mgsi/claude-code/cli.js:2213:112\\\\\\\\n    at async VuB (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_nnq5/claude-code/cli.js:3056:4)\\\\\\\\n    at async Object.prompt (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_o7a0/claude-code/cli.js:3128:1219)\\\\\\\\n    at async DRB (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_3w11/claude-code/cli.js:1733:191)\\\\\\\\n    at async Promise.all (index 0)\\\\\\\\n    at async Promise.all (index 0)\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"2025-08-09T03:39:39.593Z\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"error\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Error: Agent file /Users/bpruss/repos/cdc/cdc-devtools/.claude/agents/AGENT_REGISTRY.md is missing required 'name' in frontmatter\\\\\\\\n    at OY8 (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_cw8s/claude-code/cli.js:2213:1812)\\\\\\\\n    at file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_verz/claude-code/cli.js:2213:333\\\\\\\\n    at Array.map (\\\\u003canonymous\\\\u003e)\\\\\\\\n    at file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_oc44/claude-code/cli.js:2213:269\\\\\\\\n    at async file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_ivou/claude-code/cli.js:2213:112\\\\\\\\n    at async VuB (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_ees0/claude-code/cli.js:3056:4)\\\\\\\\n    at async Object.prompt (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_hks6/claude-code/cli.js:3128:1219)\\\\\\\\n    at async DRB (file:///opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/@anthropic-ai_grv8/claude-code/c