\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"ededed\\\",\\\"default\\\":false,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYfVw\\\"}],\\\"comments\\\":1,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T00:23:16Z\\\",\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-07-04T00:23:17Z\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/issues/3\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/issues/3\\\",\\\"comments_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/issues/3/comments\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/issues/3/events\\\",\\\"labels_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/issues/3/labels{/name}\\\",\\\"repository_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code\\\",\\\"reactions\\\":{\\\"total_count\\\":0,\\\"+1\\\":0,\\\"-1\\\":0,\\\"laugh\\\":0,\\\"confused\\\":0,\\\"heart\\\":0,\\\"hooray\\\":0,\\\"rocket\\\":0,\\\"eyes\\\":0,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/issues/3/reactions\\\"},\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"I_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAABHoVCMQ\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4807017059,\\\"number\\\":4,\\\"state\\\":\\\"open\\\",\\\"locked\\\":false,\\\"title\\\":\\\"[BUG] Custom agent tool restrictions not enforced - agents have full tool access regardless of configuration\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"## Environment\\\\n- Platform (select one):\\\\n  - [ ] Anthropic API\\\\n  - [ ] AWS Bedrock\\\\n  - [ ] Google Vertex AI\\\\n  - [ ] Other: \\\\u003c!-- specify --\\\\u003e\\\\n- Claude CLI version: \\\\u003c!-- output of `claude --version` --\\\\u003e\\\\n- Operating System: \\\\u003c!-- e.g. macOS 14.3, Windows 11, Ubuntu 22.04 --\\\\u003e\\\\n- Terminal:  \\\\u003c!-- e.g. iTerm2, Terminal App --\\\\u003e\\\\n\\\\n## Bug Description\\\\n\\\\u003c!-- A clear and concise description of the bug --\\\\u003e\\\\n\\\\n## Steps to Reproduce\\\\n  1. Create a custom agent at .claude/agents/jarvis.md with restricted tool access:\\\\n  ---\\\\n  name: jarvis\\\\n  description: Routes user requests to appropriate specialized agents\\\\n  tools: Task\\\\n  model: opus\\\\n  ---\\\\n  2. Invoke the agent using @agent-jarvis_5pon or through the Task tool\\\\n  3. The agent executes with full tool access instead of being restricted to only the Task tool\\\\n\\\\n## Expected Behavior\\\\n  - Agent configured with tools: Task should ONLY be able to use the Task tool\\\\n  - Attempting to use other tools (Read, Bash, Grep, etc.) should fail with a permission error\\\\n  - The agent should be forced to delegate work to other agents via the Task tool\\\\n\\\\n## Actual Behavior\\\\n  - Agent configured with tools: Task can use ALL tools (Read, Bash, Grep, Write, etc.)\\\\n  - The agent performs work directly instead of routing through specialized agents\\\\n  - Tool restrictions in the agent configuration are completely ignored\\\\n\\\\n## Additional Context\\\\nThis breaks the principle of least privilege and defeats the purpose of having specialized agents with limited capabilities. For example, a routing/orchestrator agent (jarvis) that should only coordinate other agents is able to perform all\\\\n  operations directly, violating its intended design as a pure orchestrator.\\\\n\\\\n  Configuration file example (.claude/agents/jarvis.md):\\\\n  ---\\\\n  name: jarvis\\\\n  description: Routes user requests to appropriate specialized agents\\\\n  tools: Task  # Should restrict to ONLY Task tool\\\\n  model: opus\\\\n  ---\\\\n\\\\n  # Agent instructions stating it should only route, never do work directly\\\\n\\\\n  Observed behavior: Despite tools: Task configuration, the agent can execute Bash commands, read files, and perform all operations that should be restricted.\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":11413102134,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/labels/bug\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"bug\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"d73a4a\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Something isn't working\\\",\\\"default\\\":true,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYeNg\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":11413102320,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/labels/area:core\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"area:core\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"ededed\\\",\\\"default\\\":false,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYe8A\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":11413102423,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/labels/area:tools\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"area:tools\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"ededed\\\",\\\"default\\\":false,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOTNEKgM8AAAACqEYfVw\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":11413102495,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/repos/mangowhoiscloud/claude-code/labels/area:security\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"area:security\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"ededed\\\",\\\"default\\\":fal