ode v70 and v71 but are completely missing in v72.\\\\n\\\\n  Environment:\\\\n  - Working: v70 and v71\\\\n  - Broken: v72\\\\n  - OS: macOS\\\\n\\\\n  Steps to Reproduce:\\\\n  1. v70/v71: Type @ → agents appear ✅\\\\n  2. v72: Type @ → NO agents appear ❌\\\\n\\\\n  Impact:\\\\n  Cannot access agents via @ commands including @agent-master-orchestrator_9p5y. Task tool works but @ interface is broken.\\\\n\\\\n  Evidence:\\\\n  - Multiple Claude Code instances confirm issue\\\\n  - Sessions on v70/v71 still work\\\\n  - Only new sessions on v72 affected\\\\n\\\\n  This is a regression between v71 and v72. Please fix or allow downgrade.\\\\n\\\\n**Environment Info**\\\\n- Platform: darwin\\\\n- Terminal: cursor\\\\n- Version: 1.0.70\\\\n- Feedback ID: ce01e968-2b13-4f38-9476-b8259df1d748\\\\n\\\\nThank you very much in advance and this awesome tool ! \\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/o