or about tool uses and finally I tried just quitting claude and starting a new context without using -resume.\\\\n\\\\n**Environment Info**\\\\n- Platform: darwin\\\\n- Terminal: Apple_Terminal\\\\n- Version: 1.0.72\\\\n- Feedback ID: c2aec1a9-6adc-42db-bf98-d193be52208c\\\\n\\\\n**Errors**\\\\n```json\\\\n⎿ API Error: 400 {\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"error\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"error\\\\\\\":{\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"invalid_request_error\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"message\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"messages.255: `tool_use` ids \\\\n    were found without `tool_result` blocks immediately after: toolu_015ZXgypVKGqFDCB2TtgNgSA. Each `tool_use` block \\\\n    must have a corresponding `tool_result` block in the next message.\\\\\\\"}}\\\\n\\\\n```\\\\n\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/gists{/gist_id}\\\",\\\"organizations_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/orgs\\\",\\\"received_events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/received_events\\\",\\\"repos_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/repos\\\",\\\"starred_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/starred{/owner}{/repo}\\\",\\\"subscriptions_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/subscriptions\\\"},\\\"comments\\