      "result": "{\"meta\": null, \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"{\\\"id\\\":4807048080,\\\"number\\\":54,\\\"state\\\":\\\"open\\\",\\\"locked\\\":false,\\\"title\\\":\\\"Document label organization for better visual organization: label guide\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"## Problem\\\\n\\\\nThe repository has many labels spanning issue-type, platform, area, status, and performance categories, but there is no central label documentation. Without label documentation, contributors have less guidance on how labels support visual organization, a label guide, and overall issue organization.\\\\n\\\\n## Proposed Solution\\\\n\\\\nCreate a comprehensive label guide for the different label categories in the repository. The guide should document every label, define its category and purpose, and explain how labels should be used for better visual organization and consistent organization.\\\\n\\\\n## Benefits\\\\n\\\\n- Improved visual organization across issues and pull requests.\\\\n- Easier issue triage because maintainers can find the right label guide and labels quickly.\\\\n- Better organization through consistent label documentation.\\\\n\\\\nKeywords: label documentation, visual organization, label guide, organization\\\",\\\"author_association\\\":\\\"OWNER\\\",\\\"user\\\":{\\\"login\\\":\\\"mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"id\\\":191002565,\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"U_kgDOC2J3xQ\\\",\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/191002565?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"gravatar_id\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud\\\",\\\"events_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/events{/privacy}\\\",\\\"following_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/following{/other_user}\\\",\\\"followers_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com/users/mangowhoiscloud/followers\\\",\\\"gists_url\\\":\\\"https://api.github.com